Eh, this was rather decent. Masahiro Sakurai keeps things funny with his unmatched wit. Plus, the Cuphead outfit is nice.

I don't love Byleth or the fact that Fire Emblem has eight reps now, but whatever. I thought this presentation was a teensy bit more enjoyable than the Terry Direct. As such, I will leave a like to be a "good boy". 🤗

Hearing Sakurai (or his translator) scream the names of each DLC fighter as he self-destructs with them was my highlight.
